data.description: Subject-to Financing, no credit check Financing, with at least $115k down, at approximately less than 4% rate. After-Repair-Value approximately $650,000 or more based on recent neighborhood comparable sales. Eagerly awaiting an investor or buyer to revive its charm. This property features: sits on a sprawling acre lot, offering limitless possibilities for the next owner with a vision. Boasting over 3200 SQ FT, including a spacious an approximately 600-SQ FT garage (not included in the SQ FT) and a pool awaiting rejuvenation, this residence has potential. Although SOLD in AS-IS condition, the property, along with the pool and hot tub, is ready for transformation. The seller to make NO REPAIRS, but still an ideal opportunity for cash buyers, hard money, renovation loans ONLY. This home has the potential to allow buyers to infuse their unique style through renovations. This home is a sound investment with a canvas for personalization. Seize the chance to breathe new life into this home.
